2013;;Red Obsession;;Australian;;David Roach;;Includes interview with winemakers from around the world;;documentary;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Red_Obsession;;Red Obsession takes the audience on a journey from Bordeaux to China, where winemakers, wine critics and wine lovers, are interviewed. The trends of the wine industry are also examined, with occasional narration provided by Russell Crowe.[1]